11
00:02:32,100 --> 00:02:32,920
Well, you know...

12
00:02:36,140 --> 00:02:39,700
It's strange for a boy and a girl to eat together!

13
00:02:40,540 --> 00:02:42,040
Why is it strange?

14
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:43,170
You see,

15
00:02:43,170 --> 00:02:44,930
Because we're not dating...{We haven't start going out together yet...}

16
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:48,050
What I'm saying is, you should eat together with your friends!

17
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:54,990
By the way...

18
00:02:55,380 --> 00:02:55,960
Eh?

19
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:58,950
Did you hear anything from your brother?

20
00:02:58,950 --> 00:03:00,080
About what?

21
00:03:00,260 --> 00:03:02,250
Oh, nothing really.

22
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:03,650
After school...

23
00:03:03,650 --> 00:03:04,160
Eh?

24
00:03:04,740 --> 00:03:06,090
Why don't we go home together?

25
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:09,650
I can't! I have dance practice today!

26
00:03:10,610 --> 00:03:12,200
For the Mugiha festival?

27
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:13,760
Y- Yeah...

28
00:03:14,130 --> 00:03:17,130
Awesome! You're a dancer?!

29
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:18,460
Dancer...

30
00:03:18,670 --> 00:03:22,180
Something lovely like that! Why'd you keep it a secret from me?

31
00:03:22,700 --> 00:03:24,930
Not like I was actually hiding it...

32
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:28,040
Besides, I am not dancing because I like it.

33
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:45,550
Tomoyo, you're late.

34
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:03,190
Here.

35
00:04:05,170 --> 00:04:08,750
Friends always exchange their side dishes with each other.

36
00:04:16,940 --> 00:04:20,500
Sorry I'm late! There were lots of people at the snack bar!

37
00:04:21,650 --> 00:04:25,340
Err, Isurugi Noe-san, this is Kurobe Tomoyo.

38
00:04:47,570 --> 00:04:48,470
Are you going home?

39
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:51,300
We don't have club activities today.

40
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:52,970
I see...

41
00:04:53,570 --> 00:04:54,320
Then...

42
00:05:02,530 --> 00:05:05,110
Even though he told me he has practice...

43
00:05:06,090 --> 00:05:07,080
Shin-!

44
00:05:11,590 --> 00:05:13,830
It's going pretty well for him, I must say.

45
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:18,220
If it goes well, maybe the four of us could go out together next time.

46
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:20,220
Kind of like a group date...

47
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,440
Hey, where should we go?

48
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,380
Anywhere's fine.

49
00:05:25,620 --> 00:05:27,120
What's with that?

50
00:05:28,020 --> 00:05:30,800
Hey, isn't that a new sweater?

51
00:05:31,050 --> 00:05:33,520
Yup, how observant of you.

52
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:35,650
Told you to leave it to me!

53
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:38,740
I know everything about Aiko, you see!

54
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:41,290
But... isn't that one just a bit plain?

55
00:05:41,650 --> 00:05:43,480
Doesn't seem like Ai-chan's taste...

56
00:05:43,930 --> 00:05:45,290
A change is nice, occasionally.

57
00:05:45,690 --> 00:05:48,840
You could have told me, I would've gone shopping with you.

58
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:52,030
Didn't you buy that one over at that store?

59
00:05:52,660 --> 00:05:56,150
What was that store that Ai-chan likes to go again?

60
00:05:57,050 --> 00:06:01,660
Oh yeah, why don't you also buy yourself a sweater?

61
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:04,000
Since all you've been wearing is that one.

62
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,560
Sweater, huh?

63
00:06:06,530 --> 00:06:10,320
"If I'm to get another one, it'd sure be nice if it was one that Ai-chan made..."

64
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:12,470
Or, that's what I want to say.

65
00:06:14,330 --> 00:06:15,350
Sure.

66
00:06:15,350 --> 00:06:17,130
Eh? Really?!

67
00:06:17,650 --> 00:06:18,750
YES!!

68
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,910
