105
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,280
I understand.

106
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:39,590
That's a lot.

107
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:42,850
Yup, but I can't eat with boys.

108
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:45,510
Oh, is that so...

109
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:47,480
They're all liars.

110
00:09:47,870 --> 00:09:49,600
It's not actually red.

111
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:52,500
They probably added some dye.

112
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,900
Captain Takaoka...

113
00:10:25,190 --> 00:10:26,370
Lunch practice?

114
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,450
Yup.

115
00:10:27,810 --> 00:10:28,880
Just Hiromi?

116
00:10:29,410 --> 00:10:30,300
Yup...

117
00:10:30,980 --> 00:10:34,680
Don't you think that Hiromi's been pushing herself too hard recently?

118
00:10:47,590 --> 00:10:49,820
Yup, let's do this.

119
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:45,470
Geez... How did you find out about this place?

120
00:11:45,470 --> 00:11:47,100
You were just like Raigou-maru!

121
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:50,810
Looking cool, courageous, shining bright!

122
00:11:51,430 --> 00:11:52,930
Is that so?

123
00:11:52,930 --> 00:11:54,160
Later, bocchan!

124
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:55,600
Oh, thanks for coming!

125
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:57,610
Come on, over here.

126
00:12:07,470 --> 00:12:09,360
Hey, Shinichirou.

127
00:12:11,050 --> 00:12:14,030
It's fine if I eat with guys once in a while, right?

128
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,770
Oh, you can't eat that one.

129
00:12:26,810 --> 00:12:31,570
You will only lie more if you eat food that rips people off.

130
00:12:31,570 --> 00:12:32,740
Lie?

131
00:12:32,740 --> 00:12:35,430
Sausages aren't actually red.

132
00:12:35,430 --> 00:12:37,520
But you made this...

133
00:12:38,430 --> 00:12:43,890
I nearly misunderstood Shinichirou...

134
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:49,370
But, I got it wrong. I can eat with Shinichirou!

135
00:12:50,860 --> 00:12:54,160
Shinichirou's a person who can shed precious tears.

136
00:12:56,650 --> 00:12:58,100
Tears, huh?

137
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:02,480
But, how are you going to turn my tears into yours?

138
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,940
There's still quite a lot to do.

139
00:13:05,930 --> 00:13:08,460
But, granny did it on me this way.

140
00:13:15,470 --> 00:13:18,750
"Following the windy night,"

141
00:13:19,330 --> 00:13:21,440
