162
00:14:48,890 --> 00:14:51,550
That girl is quite cute.

163
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:56,200
Alright, then.

164
00:14:58,090 --> 00:14:59,660
Hey, hold on!

165
00:15:08,370 --> 00:15:10,630
Dammit, just what's with that guy?

166
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:14,140
Is he retarded or something?

167
00:15:17,530 --> 00:15:20,880
